      <guid>https://sjkiss.github.io/project/data/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a movement in the natural and social sciences to increase the reliability and reproducibility of peer-reviewed research. One of the main endeavours in this initiative is to make data and code publicly available for replication and scrutiny. I&amp;rsquo;ve set up my own dataverse and here you&amp;rsquo;ll find links to some of my datasets.&lt;/p&gt;
